{
  "stem": "13469.8",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And of course, I immediately looked for souvenirs, having been well trained, perhaps organizing as we used to call it, which I forgot in our story, and also from my year of student days where we went around the country with table tennis teams.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were well-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well aware of finding souvenirs from various places.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I immediately looked for anything with Buckingham Palace on it, but there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They obviously had people like me there before at the Palace, you see, and there was nothing really worth taking.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was nothing to eat or drink.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And in fact, I was-- and Corinne, we were all in Buckingham Palace for the best part of three hours and we never had anything to eat or drink during that whole period there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in my story, I usually say that we had more at Belsen than we had in Buckingham Palace kind of thing, but perhaps you ought to scrub that out.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so we waited in this room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And not even the lavatory paper had On Her Majesty's Service or anything on it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was just blank.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was-- it was a big disappointment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we waited in this long room for ages and ages and ages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "What we hadn't realized, or I hadn't realized, not being very familiar with this kind of situation, was that the knights were done first and it was done in ever-decreasing order, obviously.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Corinne and Judith and Nick saw everything, saw the knights being knighted and the other high-level people, Waldegrave and all kinds of people who were on that day being done.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were just standing in there waiting and waiting.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
